router-tab.description:

👨‍💻 GitHub: https://github.com/bhuh12/vue-router-tab 
📝 Documentation: https://bhuh12.github.io/vue-router-tab/

🦄 Gitee: https://gitee.com/bhuh12/vue-router-tab 
📝 文档: https://bhuh12.gitee.io/vue-router-tab/zh/ 
📺 演示: https://bhuh12.gitee.io/vue-router-tab/demo/
